**Design**
Introduce explicit patch enums to make invalid states unrepresentable (typestate):
- WorkflowPatch::{NoChange, SetStatus{status, closed_reason, closed_on_branch}}
- ClaimPatch::{NoChange, Clear, Set{assignee, expires}}
Convert WireBeadPatch to carry these in a backward-compatible way or add validated newtypes (ValidatedBeadPatch) used by encoder/mutation_engine.

Update validate_bead_patch_semantics to reject impossible explicit claim combos if full typestate is too invasive. Ensure apply remains total for all explicit combinations allowed by validator.
